### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@unitId = {{createUnit.response.body.id}}

### 1. Crear Unidad (Hora)
# @name createUnit
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/service-units
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hora",
  "abbreviation": "hr"
}

### 2. Crear Unidad (Metro Cuadrado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/service-units
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Metro Cuadrado",
  "abbreviation": "m2"
}

### 3. Obtener Todas las Unidades
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/service-units

### 4. Obtener por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/service-units/{{unitId}}

### 5. Actualizar Unidad
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/service-units/{{unitId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Horas"
}

### 6. Eliminar Unidad
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/service-units/{{unitId}}
